quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  4,1,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe, hulee Joomi mon, ko KaŇčko Woni Tagir…óo on e woŇčkii wooti ; ko woni ben mon Aadama, O Tagi immorde e Aadama sonna makko Hawwaa' yumma on, O Saaki immorde e …ďen …ói…óo nder leydi ndin yim…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe ; worbe e rew…ďe. Hulee Alla on Mo yoga mon tororta yoya tuma ontigi wi'ata : "Mi torike ma fii Alla wa…óam huunde kaari". Hulee ta∆īugol en…óammaaje …óen humindir…óe on. Pellet, Alla Laatike e dow moo…óon Deeno ; hay huunde e golle mon …óen laawotaako Mo, O Moftay…óe fow O Yo…ďita on …óe."
  4,2,"Onon kaliifaa…ďe, jonnitee alyatiimaa…ďe …ďen jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen no timmiri si …ďe hellifaama, wata on wa…ótitir haraamu on ko dagii ; ko …óum woni ∆īettugol jawle ma…ď…ďe laa…ďu…óe …óen jillindiron e jawle mon …óen, wata on huuwu …óum ; pellet, huuwugol …óum laatike bakkaatu maw…óo ka Alla."
  4,3,"Si on hulii roŇčkugol nun…óude alyatiimaa…ďe …ďen tammbiti…óon si on resii …ďe, wano hulugol wata on roŇčku timminnde teŇče ma…ď…ďe …óen maa bonagol e ma…ď…ďe, haray tertee …ďe reson …ďen laa…ďu…ďe e sonnaa…ďe goo ko woori …ďe, si …óon yi…ói on resay …ói…óo maa tato maa nayo. Si on hulii nde roŇčkoton nun…óude hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, haray resee gooto maa dakmitoron …ďen …ďe jeyru…óon √Īaame moo…óon ; tawde wonaa ko wa…ó…óanii kon …ďeya sonnaa…ďe e haqqeeji wa…ó…óii …ďen …óon. Ko jaŇčtaa koo e oo Aaya fii fiyaake alyatiimaa…ďe …ďen e yonndinorgol sonnaajo gooto maa dakmitora hor…ďe …ďen, …ďuri …ďa…ótaade on nde on oo√Īo."
  4,4,"Jonnitiree rew…ďe …ďen teŇče …óen dokkal wa…ó…óingal. Si …ďe anniyoranike on woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin go…ó…óum e …óen teŇče ko aldaa e waawneede, haray √Īaamee …óum, no newanii on laa…ďani on."
  4,5,"Onon fewjoo…ďe, wata on jonnu jawle …óen on mo waawaa firlitaade fii majje, …óen jawle, Alla Wa…óiranii on …óe dartor…óe nguurdam e fiyakuuji jeyaa…ďe …ďen, …ďee …óoo non hanndaa e kippugol reena jawle. √Ďamminee e majje holtinon …ďe, wowlanon …ďe konngol mo∆ī∆īol, fodon …ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri wonnde on jonnitay…ďe jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen si …ďe hellifaama."
  4,6,"Onon fewjoo…ďe, jarribee alyatiimaa…ďe …ďen si …ďe hellifaama, jonnon…ďe see…óa e jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďe haajitora, si …ďe haajitorii…óe no haaniri, fee√Īanii on wonnde …ďe ∆īo∆īii ; haray jonnitee …ďe jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen no timmiri.Wata on √Īaamir jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen fantingol …ďuri ko Alla Daginani on haajitorgol e majje, wata on yaccor √Īaamugol …óe fii wata …ďe hellife …ďe henndoo…óe. Kala e mon taw…óo ko jogii…óo jawdi, yo o ha…óito ∆īettugol jawdi alyatiima. Kala e mon kadi taw…óo ko waasiraa…óo jawdi, yo o haajitor yeru makko on. Si …ďe hellifaama on jonnitii…ďe jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen, seedinee e kon ko jonnitoton fii reenugol haqqeeji …óin e fii wata on lurru. Alla Yonii Seedii…óo e …óum, Hasboowo jeyaa…ďe …ďen e golle ma…ď…ďe."